title: Club not showing up
body: All of my friends see me as a club leader, but I am not in any clubs and my clan tag doesnt show up.  Any help would be appreciated.

replies.body: Shoot me the name of that club and I'll get the poros on it! {{summoner:31}}
Same thing happened to me. My in game name is Mister Oswald and the club name is DirtyAfricans
